Each MINC file is named [NAME].mnc, where [NAME].dcm is the name of the first DICOM file in each series. Assumes data is unsigned 16-bit grayscale. The orientation of the MINC image volume is the same as the orientation of the DICOM image volume.

translate.description: Groups all the DICOM files into series and converts each DICOM file series into a MINC file. Each MINC file is named [NAME].mnc, where [NAME].dcm is the name of the first DICOM file in each series. Assumes data is unsigned 16-bit grayscale. The orientation of the MINC image volume is the same as the orientation of the DICOM image volume.
